<br>
I am about to get DSL (finally offered in my area) and am planning on getting a router to hook up both my computers to it. Problem is I know basically nothing about routers. So I have a couple of ?'s<br>
<br>
1. Are there some name brands that I should or should not buy?<br>
<br>
2. Is there a difference between them? Does a more expensive one actually perform better?<br>
<br>
3. I was thinking of going Wireless, is that a bad idea? Good idea?<br>
<br>
4. If I go wireless do your answers for ?'s 1 and 2 change?<br>
<br>
Basically any information anyone has would be greatly appreciated. Thanks <br>
